<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>In Tesla and SolarCity Deal, a Glimpse of Musk&#8217;s Clean-Energy Aspirations</strong> Boards of both companies approved a $2.6 billion merger, putting their faith in Elon Musk&#8217;s idea of a clean-energy powerhouse.<br />
