<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Tesla-SolarCity Deal Could Distract the Carmaker</strong> The $2.6 billion purchase of SolarCity, a solar-panel installer, comes at a crucial time for a company with lofty goals and a habit of missing them.<br />
