<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><a href="//p.nytimes.com/email/re?location=vzewYO/FHLTwPZVO2nH9zd3pqc9G7QpdPk3reFpveyN4LX2H7iMYPKsKmghXRLWIDCYxX7RKlAQzGzkUp5o6MQTPBh4sEGhESGZHJOZCzESnF+GIlz7Z/9olTeqaELbs4Z2UzLmdR4Oz2+JVfMnyKS2SIFAUQ2Yeq7QPfEx+0yZGVypokOY2Bo5ck+IEwtdVGC5QbtMI72g=&amp;campaign_id=97&amp;instance_id=79976&amp;segment_id=93081&amp;user_id=a17d64ad249adfd588c6df81d8c6c5b4&amp;regi_id=72489293">LEGAL/REGULATORY Â»</a></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>South Korea Bars Volkswagen From Selling 80 Models in Country</strong> Penalties include a $16 million fine for the German automaker, which prosecutors said falsified emissions and noise-level documentation.<br />
<a href="//p.nytimes.com/email/re?location=4z5Q7LhI+KVBjmEgFdYACPLKh239P3pgf8jIzNgNYUnezDmuqSZfyENg/sxDfBOA8Ncp2zHGvI1risOAo5Rk/n/43EfGx+aU5Qx1FD+mmQCea+1wccOeaq0RplPzH3rXryjo99Wni1qFfyL2sEuvM00x2580d6IaEgS/pNhLRLPzEgyUvahsNw==&amp;campaign_id=97&amp;instance_id=79976&amp;segment_id=93081&amp;user_id=a17d64ad249adfd588c6df81d8c6c5b4&amp;regi_id=72489293">NYT Â»</a></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Supreme Court Could Redefine Insider Trading Law</strong> The court will decide what benefit must be provided to prove a quid pro quo arrangement, and it could take insider trading law in a new direction.<br />
<a href="//p.nytimes.com/email/re?location=4z5Q7LhI+KVBjmEgFdYACPLKh239P3pgf8jIzNgNYUkX6jrpfwo+Eh/ZqTf6HH1ewjFIrcjBSVC3RN2tXLc4984w/SqJmSxvywQSf3pEsbZLLdvfjgbY7I+trlEmQwZ4iZqsxUOaI+v1hvswm446ZmIcSJMwNHhC5PXEvEFZv1yZjJVJsCASI6ckg7fCuLwi&amp;campaign_id=97&amp;instance_id=79976&amp;segment_id=93081&amp;user_id=a17d64ad249adfd588c6df81d8c6c5b4&amp;regi_id=72489293">NYT Â»</a></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>A United Effort to Overhaul Corporate Governance</strong> A recently released list of common sense boardroom principles is intended to stir conversation in the business community and stimulate economic growth.<br />
<a href="//p.nytimes.com/email/re?location=4z5Q7LhI+KVBjmEgFdYACPLKh239P3pgf8jIzNgNYUkX6jrpfwo+Eh/ZqTf6HH1eRUAe3/1a5hBCO1xuKCJQKEy4Z4I2NubWdiyqA0qYK2JfXnp1VVqWQ/60V+DsOlHrhGJHooElKS372kQfK/cOwQ61h3EbujqYW8B1yYb1I7nNpDcAfQx39mIATEYVfQ6A&amp;campaign_id=97&amp;instance_id=79976&amp;segment_id=93081&amp;user_id=a17d64ad249adfd588c6df81d8c6c5b4&amp;regi_id=72489293">NYT Â»</a></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Theranos, Embattled Laboratory, Shifts to Medical Machines</strong> Elizabeth Holmes, chief executive, introduced technology called the miniLab, suggesting a new business model for the embattled blood-testing company.<br />
<a href="//p.nytimes.com/email/re?location=4z5Q7LhI+KVBjmEgFdYACPLKh239P3pgf8jIzNgNYUkX6jrpfwo+Ek9c0eHxhbBGubYK990V1k4uGlFXlANsRMgULoG+RrXt0tw3BeNM85+w9yKmwZF5RQFndlhQDA8G1V5ZfUk6YcD1hvswm446ZmIcSJMwNHhC5PXEvEFZv1yZjJVJsCASI6ckg7fCuLwi&amp;campaign_id=97&amp;instance_id=79976&amp;segment_id=93081&amp;user_id=a17d64ad249adfd588c6df81d8c6c5b4&amp;regi_id=72489293">NYT Â»</a></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Nick Denton Files for Bankruptcy, Just Weeks After Gawker Did</strong> The long-anticipated move protects the media company&#8217;s founder from the $115 million legal judgment awarded to Hulk Hogan, who won an invasion-of-privacy lawsuit against Gawker.<br />
<a href="//p.nytimes.com/email/re?location=4z5Q7LhI+KVBjmEgFdYACPLKh239P3pgf8jIzNgNYUkX6jrpfwo+EpqtlFrC29B4A8J4gKx3IwG08yCIaTB8DS/Gugjo5SXFoZyFLtI9xTEtkiBQFENmHqu0D3xMftMmRlcqaJDmNgaOXJPiBMLXVRguUG7TCO9o&amp;campaign_id=97&amp;instance_id=79976&amp;segment_id=93081&amp;user_id=a17d64ad249adfd588c6df81d8c6c5b4&amp;regi_id=72489293">NYT Â»</a></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>F.B.I. Employee Pleads Guilty to Acting as an Agent of China</strong> The employee, Kun Shan Chun, who worked in the bureau&#8217;s New York office, had been accused of lying about his relationship with a Chinese technology company and various Chinese associates.<br />
<a href="//p.nytimes.com/email/re?location=4z5Q7LhI+KVBjmEgFdYACPLKh239P3pgf8jIzNgNYUnhKjn7/eo6/xpUpxmkCM0qJWg0fbei0JGN06Oib4J1FKLKqxBSdGt8gKul8130ENhka7Rry11ChdqWcjHFHeMWV8O0cZg0XE372kQfK/cOwQ61h3EbujqYW8B1yYb1I7nNpDcAfQx39mIATEYVfQ6A&amp;campaign_id=97&amp;instance_id=79976&amp;segment_id=93081&amp;user_id=a17d64ad249adfd588c6df81d8c6c5b4&amp;regi_id=72489293">NYT Â»</a></p>
