<a href="//p.nytimes.com/email/re?location=4z5Q7LhI+KVBjmEgFdYACPLKh239P3pgf8jIzNgNYUks4mcTb1RVf0bFovNpYh4Pf/YIKuou6etdXjc1mlu7qxezNBfG79qa4JPFqjSXf606O1j8b4MuoBCrUreCMt53HM4I/hop02b+UkknS5UBbEz46ihn6pEKV+eS7jIzsfTqGQT89fPFClPUldBuw9i0yxcN6+WfmQo=&amp;campaign_id=97&amp;instance_id=79976&amp;segment_id=93081&amp;user_id=a17d64ad249adfd588c6df81d8c6c5b4&amp;regi_id=72489293">NYT Â»</a></p>
